                      <h4 class="dp-po-post-content-note-title">
                        <i class="dp-po-icon fal fa-info-circle"></i> Note</h4>

                      <p>Account information is sent one-way, from the LDAP directory to Deskpro only. As a result, if
                        an
                        account was created via LDAP, you should reset its password, change its primary email address or
                        delete it from within the LDAP directory, not from within Deskpro.</p>
                    </div>


                    <p>The LDAP Authentication app enables you to create user and/or agent accounts from LDAP user
                      records.</p>

